{"tid":1010135,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★無家者歎新年無意義，五、六十年代賣白粉曾經過百萬家財","createTime":"2019-02-05T17:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T04:39:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8f1d781152eca0581b712da714839225fc996000","tid":1010135,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T17:19:42.000Z","msg":"78歲的露宿者水哥指，早前政府人員曾前來公園張貼告示，並意圖將他們部分物件搬出公園外行人路，但經教會及協助他們的組織交涉後，政府已停止行動，亦沒有趕他們離場。水哥指，不擔心被趕走，如果被趕亦會到其他地方如路邊及貨車頂等露宿。<br />\n<br />\n水哥稱自己已經露宿了數十年，<span style=\"color: red;\">五、六十年代經歷當黑社會賣白粉的日子，曾經擁有過百萬家財</span>，但當時不懂珍惜，花盡積蓄賭博及吸毒，「搵兩萬使三萬，搵三萬使五萬，宜家梗係後悔啦！嘢又做唔到，行都行唔到」水哥指自己已一把年紀，新年對他並沒有特別意義，今日年初一有教會前來向露宿者派年糕及蘿蔔糕等，「起碼叫有得食先」。水哥又指不希望上樓，「我都就嚟死，有邊度就瞓邊度啦」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2408960/org/36263e8f5c6f66b0c92eb584d47f72f8.jpg/W2ZeJiVylX49Ni3a9sZ9CCf6gKE7yKF81v6sAPz-rAA?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2408960%2Forg%2F36263e8f5c6f66b0c92eb584d47f72f8.jpg%2FW2ZeJiVylX49Ni3a9sZ9CCf6gKE7yKF81v6sAPz-rAA%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=9950ab26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/291905/%E8%B1%AC%E5%B9%B42019-%E7%84%A1%E5%AE%B6%E8%80%85%E6%AD%8E%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4%E7%84%A1%E6%84%8F%E7%BE%A9-%E7%8D%B2%E7%BE%A9%E5%B7%A5%E6%B4%BE%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9-%E8%B5%B7%E7%A2%BC%E6%9C%89%E5%BE%97%E9%A3%9F%E5%85%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F291905%2F%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E5%25B9%25B42019-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%25AD%258E%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2584%258F%25E7%25BE%25A9-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E9%25A3%259F%25E7%2589%25A9-%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25BE%2597%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%2585%2588&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTCgGTjEty4RfxMaQWzCDCUQ%3D&h=d10d3866\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%